# KooliHub Design Token System

## Overview
Centralized design token definitions for consistent UI across the application. All tokens are defined in CSS variables and extended via Tailwind config.

---

## 1. Token Architecture

### 1.1 Token Hierarchy
```
Design Tokens
├── Primitive Tokens (raw values)
│   ├── Colors (hex, hsl)
│   ├── Spacing (px, rem)
│   └── Typography (px, rem)
│
├── Semantic Tokens (purpose-based)
│   ├── --primary, --secondary
│   ├── --background, --foreground
│   └── --destructive, --muted
│
└── Component Tokens (component-specific)
    ├── --button-height
    ├── --card-radius
    └── --input-border
```

### 1.2 Token File Locations
```
client/
├── global.css           # CSS custom properties
├── lib/
│   ├── tokens.ts        # TypeScript token exports
│   └── constants.ts     # Static constants
│
tailwind.config.ts       # Tailwind extensions
```

