## 9. Token Usage Examples

### Using in Components
```typescript
import { TYPOGRAPHY, COMPONENT_SPACING, BUTTON_TOKENS } from '@/lib/tokens';

export function ExampleComponent() {
  return (
    <div className={COMPONENT_SPACING.cardPadding.md}>
      <h2 className={TYPOGRAPHY.h2}>Title</h2>
      <p className={TYPOGRAPHY.body}>Description text</p>
      <Button className={BUTTON_TOKENS.height.md}>
        Click me
      </Button>
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Using CSS Variables
```tsx
