## 10. Token Maintenance

### Adding New Tokens
1. Add to appropriate section in `global.css`
2. Add TypeScript export in `lib/tokens.ts`
3. Extend `tailwind.config.ts` if needed
4. Document in this file
5. Update component usage

### Token Naming Convention
```
[category]-[variant?]-[scale?]

Examples:
--color-primary
--color-primary-foreground
--spacing-4
--font-size-lg
--shadow-card
--radius-lg
```

